  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405470/extras/c17d2c7793701e718344592ac40af1d1.avif?t=1749383615\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405470/extras/65e56a5d9968ffc472b6255b2b96fdf0.poster.avif?t=1749383615\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405470/extras/65e56a5d9968ffc472b6255b2b96fdf0.webm?t=1749383615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405470/extras/2743abb456fd444a13984c02efd6d302.avif?t=1749383615\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keita lives in a quiet countryside town. His childhood friend, Ryoka Enomoto, is a women's basketball ace for her university.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Due to family circumstances, he needs a place to live for the summer, so he gets invited to stay at his friend Ryoka's house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend the summer exploring the area, meeting new people, and learning more about Ryoka in this slice of life RPG.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Slice of Life RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contemporary Japanese Setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a Japanese Countryside Town</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Calendar System with a Time Limit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to Know Ryoka</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405470/extras/c17d2c7793701e718344592ac40af1d1.avif?t=1749383615\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405470/extras/65e56a5d9968ffc472b6255b2b96fdf0.poster.avif?t=1749383615\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405470/extras/65e56a5d9968ffc472b6255b2b96fdf0.webm?t=1749383615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405470/extras/2743abb456fd444a13984c02efd6d302.avif?t=1749383615\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keita lives in a quiet countryside town. His childhood friend, Ryoka Enomoto, is a women's basketball ace for her university.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Due to family circumstances, he needs a place to live for the summer, so he gets invited to stay at his friend Ryoka's house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend the summer exploring the area, meeting new people, and learning more about Ryoka in this slice of life RPG.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Slice of Life RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contemporary Japanese Setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a Japanese Countryside Town</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Calendar System with a Time Limit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get to Know Ryoka</p></li></ul>",
